## Features

### Coin Flip
- Tap the **coin** or the **Flip the Coin** button
- Smooth multi-spin animation (5 half-rotations + bounce landing)
- Gold face = Heads 🪙 · Silver face = Tails 🌙

### Stats Bar
- Live animated bars showing Heads vs Tails ratio
- Flip count displayed in header

### Streak Tracking
- Detects consecutive same-result streaks (2+)
- Displays "3× Heads in a row!" with matching accent color

### History Log
- Last 20 flips shown with timestamp and flip number
- Gold/silver badges per result
- Clear button resets everything

### Persistence
- Stats + history saved to SharedPreferences (survives app restart)
- Gson used for serializing history list

---

## Design
Dark background `#0F0F14` with gold (`#F5C842`) and silver (`#B0BEC5`) as the two outcome accents. The coin switches gold/silver gradient depending on result. Stats bars and history badges adopt the same palette.
